        "Description": "For crying out loud! I moved near the\r\nShrine Ruins because it was a nice\r\nand quiet neighborhood... Now there\u0027s\r\na Great Izuchi and its little gang making\r\na ruckus. I tried to give \u0027em a piece of\r\nmy mind but they pulled their blades\r\non me! Hunter, please get rid of \u0027em!",
